Fritzi Fern https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fritzi_Fern 0 Fritzi Fern (September 19, 1901 – September 20, 1932) was a motion picture actress from Akron, Ohio. Her birth name was Fritzi Fern Blower. She was the daughter of Mrs. Hattie R. Blower. Fritzi_Fern ( September_19_,_1901 – September_20_,_1932 ) was a_motion_picture_actress from Akron , Ohio . Her_birth_name was Fritzi_Fern_Blower .
